Shout Select is a Blu-ray and DVD imprint of Shout! Factory. The label releases films hand-picked by film buffs at Shout! Factory, including acknowledged classics to cult favorites to unheralded gems.
Announced in May 2016, the label launched on August 16, 2016 with Blu-ray releases of The Adventures of Buckaroo Banzai Across the 8th Dimension and Elvis.
